        {
          "name": "1. Translate Text (English to Spanish)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}",
                "description": "Note: lowercase 'authorization' is required"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "*/*"
              },
              {
                "key": "Connection",
                "value": "keep-alive"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"data\": \"Hello, how are you today? I hope you are doing well and having a great day.\",\n  \"direction\": \"English to Spanish\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/translator",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["translator"]
            },
            "description": "Translate text from English to Spanish.\n\n**Direction Format:** `\"<source language> to <target language>\"`\n\n**Examples:**\n- `\"English to Spanish\"`\n- `\"Auto Detect to French\"`\n- `\"German to English\"`\n\n**⚠️ STREAMING ENDPOINT:** This endpoint returns a streaming response. Postman may show 'Connection closed' error.\n\n**Use curl instead:**\n```\ncurl -X POST 'https://api-qa.shothik.ai/api/translator' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -H 'Accept: */*' \\\n  -H 'Connection: keep-alive' \\\n  -H 'authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN' \\\n  --data-raw '{\"data\": \"Hello\", \"direction\": \"English to Spanish\"}'\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response (Streaming)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "Hola, ¿cómo estás hoy? Espero que estés bien y tengas un gran día."
            }
          ]
        },
