            "description": "Humanize and improve translated text by fixing grammar issues.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `data`: The translated text to humanize\n- `language`: Target language of the text\n- `mode`: Processing mode (\"Fixed\")\n- `synonym`: Synonym level (\"Basic\")\n\n**⚠️ STREAMING ENDPOINT:** This endpoint returns a streaming response."
          },
          "response": [
